Messaging Services Comparison
AWS offers three main messaging services, each designed for diffrent use cases:
Service                          Type                   How it Works
EventBridge               Event Bus                     Routes events based on 
                                                        rules to multiple targets
SNS                        Publish-subscribe                              Pushes messages to multiple subscribers at once
